Solarworld Says It Could Double U.S. Sales, to Continue Capacity Expansion

-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 
2011-03-24T12:19:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/solarworld-says-it-could-double-u-s-sales-to-continue-capacity-expansion.html
Solarworld AG (SWV)  aims to increase its
revenue this year, and will continue its capacity expansion in
module production to reach 1,400 megawatts, the company said in
a statement today.  The company “considers it possible to more than double its
sales” in the U.S., according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  